msgstr "Y-as marge (positie boven/onder links/rechts)"

msgid ""
"Vertical offset from the top or bottom edge when positioned at the top "
"centre, bottom centre, top left, bottom left, top right or bottom right."
msgstr ""
"Verticale verschuiving van de boven- of onderkant bij positionering boven "
"midden, onder midden, linksboven, linksonder, rechtsboven of rechtsonder."

